title: ASC Entente Sebkha FC
text:
ASC Entente Sebkha FC is a <a href="Mauritania">Mauritanean</a> <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> club based in <a href="Sebkha%2C%20Mauritania">Sebkha</a> a suburb of <a href="Nouakchott">Nouakchott</a>. The club plays in the Mauritanian second division.
In 2003 the team has won <a href="Coupe%20du%20Pr%C3%A9sident%20de%20la%20R%C3%A9publique">Coupe du Président de la République</a>.
Stadium.
Currently the team plays at the 1000 capacity <a href="Stade%20Cheikha%20Ould%20Bo%C3%AFdiya">Stade Cheikha Ould Boïdiya</a>.
